{"tid":474030,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"完全唔準塔羅占卜","createTime":"2017-11-19T18:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T14:36:52.000Z","uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb438774690df75eb7e8fb087a99f7a6e1ecbdd","tid":474030,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:39:57.000Z","msg":"（警告⚠️：通常唔準，算錯勿屌）<br />\n⚠️⚠️麻煩閱讀一下以下注意的事項,如果問左我唔會理你<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n1.時間性問題唔占eg.幾時結婚，幾時有女<br />\n<br />\n2未來問題唔占eg.今年12月我條仔會唔會搵翻我，下年我條仔同我會係點<br />\n<br />\n3.非自身問題唔占，eg我男朋友有無外遇，我暗戀對象喜歡我嗎<br />\n<br />\n4.XX運唔占，eg愛情運會點,學業運會點</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n5.唔一定個個占到,小弟塔羅牌占卜太垃圾一日只能占到幾個,本次開post只為測試自己準確度之用<br />\n<br />\n塔羅牌只是工具，主要用於了解自己內心，未來在你手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩提供姓名，具體問題，性別,數字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩在1-56內選擇一個數字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只回覆tg占卜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/yishioupapa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyishioupapa&d=T9%2Fd3cii%2FhqBkXIVL78ZKtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8f913a7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/yishioupapa</a>"},{"pid":"fe895b28fce4ad21585d8c69122fd5ea8de201ec","tid":474030,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:41:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://youtu.be/hBQIPHfdQv8?t=27s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhBQIPHfdQv8%3Ft%3D27s&d=T9%2Fd3cii%2FhqBkXIVL78ZKtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e6d17d8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/hBQIPHfdQv8?t=27s</a>"},{"pid":"a92ccd93b04c7d9e525985a4713e74ce5721d060","tid":474030,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b2424ad29c592bf7b8e1d9538e3d7fc2d4ff97","tid":474030,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T18:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/as